{"tid":1405704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] [超實用] 點樣最有效咁幫車軚放氣","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T15:16:11.000Z","uid":79679,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e608cea42bf3a9d2b0b7beab637b94dc7fedba30","tid":1405704,"uid":79679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">啱先發夢見到我個friend話想幫啲狗車放氣，但又唔知點做，咁啱小弟做開呢行，就醒左佢幾招</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工欲善其事 必先利其器</span></span><br />\n首先，你要買一樣叫tyre valve core wrench/removal tool嘅嘢，呢個上eBay, Amazon 好多，幾蚊就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DpD5tE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DpD5tE.png&h=50a400ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lc0f7Hp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLc0f7Hp.png&h=1f2baf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後就到放氣喇，其實車軚同單車軚基本上都大同小異，都有個打氣閥，姐係平時你擰開個蓋用黎打氣個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vx63xbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVx63xbD.png&h=675d8da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">然後佢入面仲有個芯，拎左佢出黎就可以超快咁放氣，更重要係，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇左佢就打唔翻氣入去</span></span></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個芯:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1kf732.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1kf732.png&h=0bd04c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">而且要拎佢出黎亦超簡單，只要擰開個蓋，然後用上面個工具，好似鬆螺絲將個芯鬆出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n教學影片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_zzkwL6QmlY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_zzkwL6QmlY&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUBzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=b03bd7c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_zzkwL6QmlY</a><br />\n<br />\n由<span style=\"color: blue;\">1:10</span>開始<br />\n<br />\n成本低成效高，過程10秒都唔洗，各位前線巴絲可以夢遊嗰陣練習下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b277cff66162092f43fa85336979f40cb58db6","tid":1405704,"uid":79679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e608cea42bf3a9d2b0b7beab637b94dc7fedba30","tid":1405704,"uid":79679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">啱先發夢見到我個friend話想幫啲狗車放氣，但又唔知點做，咁啱小弟做開呢行，就醒左佢幾招</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工欲善其事 必先利其器</span></span><br />\n首先，你要買一樣叫tyre valve core wrench/removal tool嘅嘢，呢個上eBay, Amazon 好多，幾蚊就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DpD5tE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DpD5tE.png&h=50a400ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lc0f7Hp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLc0f7Hp.png&h=1f2baf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後就到放氣喇，其實車軚同單車軚基本上都大同小異，都有個打氣閥，姐係平時你擰開個蓋用黎打氣個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vx63xbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVx63xbD.png&h=675d8da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">然後佢入面仲有個芯，拎左佢出黎就可以超快咁放氣，更重要係，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇左佢就打唔翻氣入去</span></span></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=